      • getPublicationKey

        public String getPublicationKey()
        Unique key of the publication within it's domain. If WebCmsPublications are not WebCmsDomainBound then the key has to be unique. Do not confuse with WebCmsObjectSuperClass.getObjectId() which is a globally unique key across all assets.

      • getArticleTemplatePage

        public WebCmsPage getArticleTemplatePage()
        Page that is considered the template for an article detail. This page should be loaded when rendering an article from this publication, and the canonicalPath of the page will be used when generating the default urls.
